name: Colour over colour
description:
This is where we are at our best
In the flow

The flow
 of colour coatin colour
Of water traveling past

In each others company
We like to work and play

Never once with a bicker or a gripe
This is our ease. 

And i know tough times are ahead
We will be pulled and stretched 
But for now we have work
And there's a summer to come

Colour over colour
Water travelling past
